    s"See for yourself. There‚Äôs a mirror over there."
    # (MC looks at himself in the mirror)"
    show sc w4eowmaskshop m13
    mc"Oh, that actually looks a lot better than I thought it would."
    s"I agree, and I think it will match very well with your outfit."
    show sc w4eowmaskshop m03
    s"Did you want to look at any of the other masks?"
    mc"No, I think I‚Äôm happy with this one."
    mc"Thanks [s_name], that was easier than I thought it would be."
    $ v_task_02_04 = True
    if persistent.v_textbox_dialogue:
        $ persistent.v_textbox_dialogue = False
        call screen scr_02_04_task_completed
        $ persistent.v_textbox_dialogue = True
    else:
        call screen scr_02_04_task_completed

    show sc w4eowmaskshop m02
    s"More than happy to help."
    show sc w4eowmaskshop m03
    s"So how did you know about this place?"
    mc"Well, your Mom told me about it when I saw her yesterday."
    show sc w4eowmaskshop m04
    s"Oh, right. I didn‚Äôt ask you how that went."
    s"Did you end up going over to her place?"
    mc"(Hmm‚Ä¶ I wonder what [s_name] will think if I were to tell her that I met with her mother up in the mountains at her workplace.)"
    if v_w4mow_ashley_night:
        # ‚ÄúAdd these lines if the player slept with Ashley‚Äù"
        mc"(She may get suspicious and ask more questions if I were to tell her the truth.)"
    menu:
        "Lie":
            show sc w4eowmaskshop m03
            $ s_points = change_stat(s_points,-10,s_name)
            mc"Uh, yeah, I just went to her house. But I wasn‚Äôt there very long." #-10 SIS POINTS"
            mc"Ashley recommended this place for me to get a mask which seems like it‚Äôs going to turn out to be a pretty good call."
            mc"She also suggested that we open the east wing of the hotel as soon as possible."
            show sc w4eowmaskshop m04
            s"(Sigh‚Ä¶)"
            s"Yeah, it seems like everyone we know is pushing for us to do that."
            s"They‚Äôre right though, we do need to get that wing open so we have a few more rooms available for our guests."
            s"We‚Äôre almost at capacity for bookings this weekend which I presume is due to the festival."
            s"We certainly could have done with some extra rooms but there‚Äôs nothing we can do about that now."
            show sc w4eowmaskshop m03
            mc"We‚Äôll make sure that we complete that task before the following weekend begins."
            show sc w4eowmaskshop m05
            s"Yeah, that‚Äôd be great if we could."
            show sc w4eowmaskshop m03
            mc"(It seems like she bought the lie.)"
            mc"(Man, I've really gotta stop lying to [s_name] as it will eventually catch up with me.)"
            if v_w4mow_ashley_night:
                mc"(But there‚Äôs no easy way for me to say, ‚ÄúOh by the way [s_name], I stayed at your Mom‚Äôs cabin and I slept in her bed.‚Äù)"
                mc"(‚ÄúAnd you can fill in the blanks from there.‚Äù)"
                mc"(Sigh‚Ä¶ Goddamnit, I am such a schmuck.)"
            show sc w4eowmaskshop m04
            s"Did she say anything else?"
        "Be honest"(wt="Best choice"):
            show sc w4eowmaskshop m03
            mc"We didn‚Äôt get to properly talk about the festival until later in the day."
            mc"I uh‚Ä¶ I went up to the mountains to visit your Mom where she works."
            show sc w4eowmaskshop m04
            s"Oh, you did?"
            mc"Yeah, I‚Äôm sorry I didn‚Äôt tell you about this sooner as we‚Äôve both had a lot going on this morning..."
            mc"And I was worried about what you would think."
            show sc w4eowmaskshop m14
            s"Well I think now is the time that you explain why you went all the way up there [y_name]."
            # (Sis‚Äô arms folded, waiting for a response)"
            show sc w4eowmaskshop m04
            mc"Here‚Äôs the thing."
            mc"Your mother had invited me to come up and see where she works a couple of times before..."
            mc"And I didn‚Äôt want to be rude by continually saying no or maybe to her."
            mc"I figured it was also the best way to get the information that we needed. As you said, Ashley can be quite persuasive and she certainly didn‚Äôt disappoint in that respect."
            show sc w4eowmaskshop m14
            s"Yeah, I know what she can be like."
            show sc w4eowmaskshop m04
            s"So what happened when you arrived up there?"
            mc"It was pretty cool actually. She showed me around her workplace and her office."
            mc"She also showed me this lookout point where you can see the entire town. It was pretty amazing I have to say."
            show sc w4eowmaskshop m15
            s"(Hmm‚Ä¶ I know that lookout point he‚Äôs referring to.)"
            show sc w4eowmaskshop m03
            mc"Oh! And before I forget..."
            mc"Your aunt Trisha suggested that we list the hotel online as one of the festival sponsors to give it some more exposure."
            mc"I was able to do that on your Mom‚Äôs computer while I was in her office."
            s"So, our hotel will be promoted at this weekend‚Äôs festival?"
            mc"It will be. I received a confirmation email this morning."
            show sc w4eowmaskshop m02
            s"That‚Äôs fantastic news [y_name]!"
            show sc w4eowmaskshop m03
            s"Why are you only telling me about this now?"
            mc"I kind of wanted it to be a surprise."
            show sc w4eowmaskshop m02
            $ s_points = change_stat(s_points,5,s_name)
            s"You‚Äôve done really well [y_name]. This could be a game-changer for us." #+5 SIS POINTS"
            show sc w4eowmaskshop m04
            s"Sorry for pushing you with questions about my mother."
            s"I guess I‚Äôm worried that she‚Äôll try and manipulate you as she did with me."
            mc"It‚Äôs okay, I understand."
            s"So what else did you and my mother discuss?"

    jump lb_w4eow_s_mc_mask_menu


label lb_w4eow_s_mc_mask_menu:
    # [The hotel / The festival] *Both options can be chosen here"
    if v_w4eow_s_mc_mask_hotel and v_w4eow_s_mc_mask_festival:
        jump lb_w4eow_s_mc_mask_menu_ending

    menu:
        "The hotel" if v_w4eow_s_mc_mask_hotel == False:
            $ v_w4eow_s_mc_mask_hotel = True
            show sc w4eowmaskshop m03
            mc"We also talked about the hotel. She suggested that we open the east wing as soon as possible."
            show sc w4eowmaskshop m04
            s"(Sigh‚Ä¶)"
            s"It seems like everyone we know is pushing for us to do that."
            s"They‚Äôre right though, we do need to get that wing open so we have a few more rooms available for our guests."
            s"We‚Äôre almost at capacity for this weekend which I presume is due to this weekend‚Äôs festival."
            s"We certainly could have done with some extra rooms but there‚Äôs nothing we can do about that now."
            show sc w4eowmaskshop m03
            mc"We‚Äôll make sure that we complete that task before the following weekend."
            show sc w4eowmaskshop m02
            s"Yeah, that‚Äôd be great."
            show sc w4eowmaskshop m03
            s"Did she say anything else?"
            jump lb_w4eow_s_mc_mask_menu
        "The festival" if v_w4eow_s_mc_mask_festival == False:
            $ v_w4eow_s_mc_mask_festival = True
            show sc w4eowmaskshop m03
            mc"We also talked about the festival."
            mc"Ashley recommended that we talk to as many people as we can during the event."
            s"How come?"
            mc"She believes that big business owners will be in attendance, and perhaps it will be a chance for us to capitalise on it for the hotel."
            mc"Seeing as your Mom usually attends every year, I figure she might be onto something with this."
            mc"She also suggested that we promote the hotel, together."
            show sc w4eowmaskshop m05
            s"Yeah, I agree."
            show sc w4eowmaskshop m03
            s"Did she say anything else?"
            jump lb_w4eow_s_mc_mask_menu



label lb_w4eow_s_mc_mask_menu_ending:
    # (scene continues)"
    mc"No, that‚Äôs it."
    show sc w4eowmaskshop m15
    s"And nothing else happened? She didn‚Äôt try and persuade you to stay any longer than you needed to up there, did she?"
    show sc w4eowmaskshop m04
    mc"(Oh man, she just had to ask that question.)"
    mc"(But why?)"
    if v_w4mow_ashley_night:
        # ‚ÄúAdd these lines if the player is ON the Ashley path, even if the MC didn‚Äôt sleep with her‚Äù"
        mc"(Is it possible that [s_name] has clued on to the fact that something‚Äôs going on between me and her mother?)"

    if v_w4mow_ashley_night == False:
        # ‚ÄúThese lines if the player chose ‚ÄúHead to the hotel‚Äù or IS NOT on the Ashley path - https://pixhost.to/show/50/235698654_screenshot0009.png‚Äù"
        show sc w4eowmaskshop m03
        mc"She did, but I politely declined her offer."
        mc"I told her that I promised to have dinner with you and that it was important for me to return to the hotel before sunset."
        # (Sis smiles) +5 SIS POINTS"
        $ s_points = change_stat(s_points,5,s_name)
        show sc w4eowmaskshop m05
        mc"I just didn‚Äôt expect it to rain on my way back."
        s"Yeah, that was very unexpected. But I‚Äôm really glad that you made it home, safe and sound."
        show sc w4eowmaskshop m04
        s"And I wish I hadn‚Äôt gone out with Ivy and Lily, or that I stood you up for dinner."
        show sc w4eowmaskshop m03
        mc"It‚Äôs cool. But we‚Äôre gonna make up for it tonight, remember?"
        show sc w4eowmaskshop m02
        s"Haha, yes we are!"
    else:
        # ‚ÄúThese lines if the player chose ‚ÄúGo with her‚Äù (they went to Ashley‚Äôs cabin) - https://pixhost.to/show/50/235698654_screenshot0009.png‚Äù"
        show sc w4eowmaskshop m03
        mc"She did, but I told her that I wasn‚Äôt interested."
        mc"It was getting late at the time and I tried to get back to the hotel because I knew that we had plans for dinner."
        mc"But by the time I returned, you were already gone."
        show sc w4eowmaskshop m04
        s"Oh‚Ä¶ Yeah, I must have been out with Ivy and Lily by then."
        mc"I guess you were."
        show sc w4eowmaskshop m15
        s"(Then again, I didn‚Äôt leave the hotel until around seven, and [y_name] hadn‚Äôt returned by that point.)"
        s"(I wonder what took him so long to come back from the mountains?)"
        show sc w4eowmaskshop m04
        mc"(Hmm‚Ä¶ I think she bought it.)"
        mc"(Man, I've really gotta stop lying to [s_name] as it will eventually catch up with me.)"
        mc"(But there‚Äôs no easy way to say, ‚ÄúOh by the way [s_name], I stayed at your Mom‚Äôs cabin and slept in her bed.‚Äù)"
        mc"(‚ÄúAnd you can fill in the blanks from there.‚Äù)"
        $ s_points = change_stat(s_points,-10,s_name)
        mc"(Sigh‚Ä¶ Goddamnit, I am such a schmuck.)"# -10 SIS POINTS"
        show sc w4eowmaskshop m05
        s"I‚Äôm just really glad that you made it home, safe and sound."
        show sc w4eowmaskshop m04
        s"And I wish I hadn‚Äôt gone out with Ivy and Lily, or that I stood you up for dinner."
        show sc w4eowmaskshop m03
        mc"It‚Äôs cool. But we‚Äôre gonna make up for it tonight, remember?"
        show sc w4eowmaskshop m02
        s"Haha, yes we are!"
        # (scene continues)"
    # (scene continues)"
    show sc w4eowmaskshop m03
    mc"Anyway, I‚Äôm going to take this mask and go and pay for it at the counter."
    mc"Thanks again for your help [s_name]."
    show sc w4eowmaskshop m05
    s"You‚Äôre welcome [y_name]. I love being the one to help you out whenever I can."
    s"I‚Äôll wait for you outside by the scooter."
    # (Sis smiles as the MC leaves to pay for the mask)"
