    k"When I don‚Äôt have to wear specific clothes at the church, yeah, I try and wear anything pink."
    k"Do you have a favourite colour?"
    mc"Oh, well, I guess if I were to choose a specific favourite colour then it would be‚Ä¶"
    # [Black / Pink / Blue]"
    menu:
