            mc"Oh, that‚Äôs good!"
            k"However, black also denotes death, fear and ignorance."
            mc"Oh, that‚Äôs bad‚Ä¶"
            $ k_points = change_stat(k_points,-2,k_name)
            k"So as you can imagine it‚Äôs not really a favourite colour of mine." #-2 KRISTINA POINTS"
            mc"No, of course not."
            mc"(Damn, that was an obvious strike out!)"
        "Pink":
            show sc w4eowmaskshop m23
