            show sc w4eowmaskshop m22
            mc"Hmm‚Ä¶ I never thought of it like that."
            mc"So do you like the colour blue as well?"
            k"It‚Äôs second to pink."
            k"Blue often symbolizes serenity, stability, inspiration, wisdom or health."
            $ k_points = change_stat(k_points,2,k_name)
            k"It‚Äôs also known to be a calming colour, and it symbolizes reliability." #+2 KRISTINA POINTS"
            mc"Oh, I never knew that."
            show sc w4eowmaskshop m26
            k"(Hmm‚Ä¶ Maybe that‚Äôs one of the reasons why I‚Äôm so drawn to [y_name]. He makes me feel calm whenever I‚Äôm around him.)"
    # (scene continues)"
    show sc w4eowmaskshop m23
