    show sc w4eowmaskshop m19
    k"That‚Äôs nice, she certainly knows her stuff."
    show sc w4eowmaskshop m17
    mc"[k_name], there‚Äôs something I‚Äôve been meaning to ask you."
    show sc w4eowmaskshop m18
